To make the counters, you need to make the variables available to the entire method. Initialize the game, win, and loss counters right after keyboard and rand:

        Scanner keyboard = new Scanner(System.in);
        Random rand = new Random();
        int gameCount = 0;
        int winCount = 0;
        //int lossCount

